curam.util.ctm.bom

Class ComparisonResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • curam.util.ctm.bom.ComparisonResult

  • public class ComparisonResult
extends java.lang.Object
    Holder class that collects the reporting data related to results after comparison. The result will containing the following information.
    • Newly added data for a new type
    • Newly added data for an existing type
    • Completely deleted data for an existing type
    • Partially deleted data for an existing type
    • Similar data set for the set of types
